title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
OB: When exporting data from a table that is located inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export should proceed without any exceptions being thrown.
SR: 1. Insert a table into a grid cell. 2. Insert another table into a different grid cell. 3. Attempt to export the data from one of the tables.
